OL,3,GUK weather for today and tomorrow
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FMorning fog clearing to leave
OL,6,Fmany places hot and sunny. Cloudier
OL,7,Ffor parts of Scotland with the risk of
OL,8,Fshowery rain in the north, which may
OL,9,Fturn heavy and thundery later. An
OL,10,Fisolated late afternoon thunderstorm
OL,11,Fmay also develop elsewhere.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FAny isolated thunderstorms
OL,14,Feasing, with most having a fine
OL,15,Fevening. Remaining largely cloudy
OL,16,Facross Scotland overnight, with a few
OL,17,Fspots of rain. Generally dry and clear
OL,18,Felsewhere. Staying warm.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
