OL,4,
OL,5,CSaturday:FRather cloudy across
OL,6,FScotland, with showery rain. Generally
OL,7,Fsunny elsewhere, but the risk of low
OL,8,Fcloud along eastern coasts of England.
OL,9,FBreezy. Hot in the west, cooler in the
OL,10,Feast.
